  power_cleaned_list,
  read_csv,
  col_type = cols(fips = col_character())
) |>
  list_rbind() |>
  clean_names()

Common cause of outages

outages |> 
1  group_by (event_category) |>
2  summarize(total_events = n()) |>
3  arrange(total_events |> desc())

Cause of longest outages

outages |> 
1  group_by (event_category) |>
2  summarize(avg_outage_length = mean(duration), total_occurences = n()) |>
3  arrange(avg_outage_length |> desc(), total_occurences)
